<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>国土报最新头条</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Fri, 24 Nov 2023 08:09:09 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>以色列边境沿线的居民全副武装，焦虑不安，正在为最坏的情况做好准备</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-24/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/armed-and-anxious-residents-along-israels-borders-are-bracing-for-the-worst/0000018b-ff81-de73-a9bb-ffe781fb0000</link><description>战争爆发以来，以色列边境居民的安全感受到严重动摇。曾经享受平静生活和田园风光的人们现在正在武装自己，想知道敌人需要多长时间才能突破脆弱的栅栏</description><pubDate>Fri, 24 Nov 2023 05:17:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-24/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/armed-and-anxious-residents-along-israels-borders-are-bracing-for-the-worst/0000018b-ff81-de73-a9bb-ffe781fb0000</guid></item><item><title>人道主义援助在停火期间进入加沙 13名人质数小时内获释</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-24/ty-article-live/cease-fire-set-to-begin-at-7-a-m-13-women-and-children-to-be-released-in-afternoon/0000018b-ff7f-d4d0-addf-ffffa24a0000</link><description>为期四天的停火于当地时间周五上午 7 点生效，第一批人质妇女和儿童将于周五下午 4 点获释 ■ 哈马斯表示将不允许红十字会探视剩余的人质 ■ ■火灾将导致救援物资进入加沙，战斗暂停，50 名人质和 150 名巴勒斯坦囚犯获释 ■ 以色列确认逮捕加沙 Al-Shifa 主任：“监督医院被用作哈马斯总部” ■ 真主党声称对以色列北部大规模火箭弹袭击负责 ■自10月7日以来，以色列至少有1,200名平民和士兵被杀，236名人质在加沙地带被扣押 ■ 哈马斯控制的卫生部：加沙有14,854人死亡</description><pubDate>Fri, 24 Nov 2023 04:11:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-24/ty-article-live/cease-fire-set-to-begin-at-7-a-m-13-women-and-children-to-be-released-in-afternoon/0000018b-ff7f-d4d0-addf-ffffa24a0000</guid></item><item><title>随着以色列进入加沙休战，内塔尼亚胡继续对国防机构发动战争</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-24/ty-article/.premium/as-israel-heads-into-gaza-truce-netanyahu-keeps-waging-war-on-the-defense-establishment/0000018b-fdd8-de73-a9bb-ffff98840000</link><description>内塔尼亚胡知道以色列国防军及其士兵将因摧毁加沙而获得赞誉，正如他明白人质协议是能够帮助他走出政治深渊的第一件事一样</description><pubDate>Fri, 24 Nov 2023 04:02:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-24/ty-article/.premium/as-israel-heads-into-gaza-truce-netanyahu-keeps-waging-war-on-the-defense-establishment/0000018b-fdd8-de73-a9bb-ffff98840000</guid></item><item><title>随着第一批人质即将获释，以色列已经在计划下一阶段的加沙战争</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-24/ty-article/.premium/israel-planning-for-stage-2-of-the-war-against-hamas-even-before-the-hostages-are-home/0000018b-fd9a-d99b-a7eb-fd9e53d40000</link><description>战斗暂停将使以色列国防军能够在加沙地带南部组织新的进攻——这可能需要几个月的时间。受西岸局势困扰 ■</description><pubDate>Fri, 24 Nov 2023 04:01:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-24/ty-article/.premium/israel-planning-for-stage-2-of-the-war-against-hamas-even-before-the-hostages-are-home/0000018b-fd9a-d99b-a7eb-fd9e53d40000</guid></item><item><title>国土报卡通</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/daily-cartoon/2023-11-24/ty-article-opinion/haaretz-cartoon/0000018b-fe51-d99b-a7eb-ffd7c5750000</link><description></description><pubDate>Thu, 23 Nov 2023 22:35:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/daily-cartoon/2023-11-24/ty-article-opinion/haaretz-cartoon/0000018b-fe51-d99b-a7eb-ffd7c5750000</guid></item><item><title>为了所有以色列人的利益，废除排他性民族国家法</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-23/ty-article-opinion/.premium/repeal-the-exclusionary-nation-state-law-for-the-sake-of-all-israelis/0000018b-fdd9-de73-a9bb-ffff291b0000</link><description></description><pubDate>Thu, 23 Nov 2023 21:41:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-23/ty-article-opinion/.premium/repeal-the-exclusionary-nation-state-law-for-the-sake-of-all-israelis/0000018b-fdd9-de73-a9bb-ffff291b0000</guid></item><item><title>感谢以色列极右翼财政部长，我们正处于经济灾难的边缘</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/editorial/2023-11-23/ty-article-opinion/thanks-to-israels-far-right-finance-minister-were-on-the-brink-of-economic-disaster/0000018b-fdb9-de0a-a18f-fffd61100000</link><description></description><pubDate>Thu, 23 Nov 2023 21:33:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/editorial/2023-11-23/ty-article-opinion/thanks-to-israels-far-right-finance-minister-were-on-the-brink-of-economic-disaster/0000018b-fdb9-de0a-a18f-fffd61100000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡的胜利不是我们的胜利</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-11-23/ty-article-opinion/.premium/netanyahus-victory-is-not-our-victory/0000018b-fd72-de0a-a18f-ff7714300000</link><description></description><pubDate>Thu, 23 Nov 2023 21:29:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-11-23/ty-article-opinion/.premium/netanyahus-victory-is-not-our-victory/0000018b-fd72-de0a-a18f-ff7714300000</guid></item><item><title>哈马斯领导人辛瓦尔正在嘲笑内塔尼亚胡</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-11-23/ty-article-opinion/.premium/hamas-leader-sinwar-is-making-laughingstock-out-of-netanyahu/0000018b-fd72-d99b-a7eb-fdf6152d0000</link><description></description><pubDate>Thu, 23 Nov 2023 21:27:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-11-23/ty-article-opinion/.premium/hamas-leader-sinwar-is-making-laughingstock-out-of-netanyahu/0000018b-fd72-d99b-a7eb-fdf6152d0000</guid></item><item><title>《国土报》如何统计 10 月 7 日哈马斯袭击事件中以色列的死亡人数</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-23/ty-article-magazine/.premium/how-haaretz-is-counting-israels-dead-from-the-october-7-hamas-attack/0000018b-d42c-d423-affb-f7afe1a70000</link><description>以下是对 10 月 7 日哈马斯袭击中以色列死难者名单的完整记录，记录了我们在新闻报道上一丝不苟、令人心力交瘁的过程：</description><pubDate>Thu, 23 Nov 2023 20:11:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-23/ty-article-magazine/.premium/how-haaretz-is-counting-israels-dead-from-the-october-7-hamas-attack/0000018b-d42c-d423-affb-f7afe1a70000</guid></item><item><title>“我们可以睡觉而不用担心死亡”：停火为加沙人带来了新鲜空气</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2023-11-23/ty-article/.premium/we-can-sleep-without-fear-of-dying-cease-fire-is-a-breath-of-fresh-air-for-gazans/0000018b-fd98-de73-a9bb-ffff81ec0000</link><description>虽然只是暂时的，但加沙居民热切地等待四天的战斗暂停，并希望这将为更长的喘息时间打开大门。 “在我们每天都处于死亡状态的一个半月之后，这是乐观的迹象——生命的迹象。”</description><pubDate>Thu, 23 Nov 2023 20:10:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2023-11-23/ty-article/.premium/we-can-sleep-without-fear-of-dying-cease-fire-is-a-breath-of-fresh-air-for-gazans/0000018b-fd98-de73-a9bb-ffff81ec0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列通讯部长威胁国土报，建议惩罚其加沙战争报道</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-23/ty-article/israels-communications-minister-threatens-haaretz-suggests-penalizing-its-war-coverage/0000018b-fd0c-de73-a9bb-ffefb9f10000</link><description>在利库德集团部长什洛莫·卡希提议对《国土报》进行经济处罚后，他称之为“谎言、失败主义宣传”，著名记者猛烈抨击内塔尼亚胡政府对以色列新闻自由的最新攻击</description><pubDate>Thu, 23 Nov 2023 18:14:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-23/ty-article/israels-communications-minister-threatens-haaretz-suggests-penalizing-its-war-coverage/0000018b-fd0c-de73-a9bb-ffefb9f10000</guid></item><item><title>“作为四个男孩的以色列母亲，军队游戏不是我想玩的”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/holylandings/2023-11-23/ty-article/.highlight/as-an-israeli-mother-of-four-boys-the-army-game-is-not-something-i-want-to-play/0000018b-fd25-d99b-a7eb-fdb77c2d0000</link><description>本周在本古里安机场：战争愈演愈烈，一位母亲担心孩子的未来，一对俄罗斯夫妇逃离另一个冲突地区</description><pubDate>Thu, 23 Nov 2023 17:29:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/holylandings/2023-11-23/ty-article/.highlight/as-an-israeli-mother-of-four-boys-the-army-game-is-not-something-i-want-to-play/0000018b-fd25-d99b-a7eb-fdb77c2d0000</guid></item><item><title>导致灾难的不是加沙脱离接触，而是内塔尼亚胡的政策</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-23/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/it-wasnt-the-gaza-disengagement-but-netanyahus-policies-that-led-to-disaster/0000018b-fcf1-de73-a9bb-fef7ab240000</link><description>追寻10月7日惨案的历史根源，我们必须回到十年前总理的决定</description><pubDate>Thu, 23 Nov 2023 17:04:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-23/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/it-wasnt-the-gaza-disengagement-but-netanyahus-policies-that-led-to-disaster/0000018b-fcf1-de73-a9bb-fef7ab240000</guid></item><item><title>西方外交官：加沙“处于医疗灾难的边缘”，有疾病爆发的迹象</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2023-11-23/ty-article/.premium/western-diplomats-gaza-on-the-verge-of-medical-catastrophe-signs-of-disease-outbreak/0000018b-fc8c-d330-a9bb-ffdeafe70000</link><description>几位接受《国土报》采访的外交官报告称，近东救济工程处警告称，儿童皮肤病爆发，胃肠道疾病病例有所增加。一位外交官警告说，加沙的医疗系统正在崩溃。 “如果发生这种情况，以色列也会受到伤害”</description><pubDate>Thu, 23 Nov 2023 16:36:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2023-11-23/ty-article/.premium/western-diplomats-gaza-on-the-verge-of-medical-catastrophe-signs-of-disease-outbreak/0000018b-fc8c-d330-a9bb-ffdeafe70000</guid></item><item><title>华盛顿特区高级自由派人士表示，不可能将美国对以色列的看法与美国人对内塔尼亚胡的看法区分开来</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-11-23/ty-article-magazine/.premium/young-democrats-are-being-failed-by-the-old-guard-warns-leading-d-c-liberal/0000018b-fc5e-d330-a9bb-ffded9a60000</link><description>美国进步中心主席帕特里克·加斯帕德告诉《国土报》，各方必须如何在以色列与哈马斯暂停的基础上再接再厉，美国是否应该对以色列的援助设定条件，以及为什么不轻视批评以色列战争的年轻民主党人</description><pubDate>Thu, 23 Nov 2023 16:36:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-11-23/ty-article-magazine/.premium/young-democrats-are-being-failed-by-the-old-guard-warns-leading-d-c-liberal/0000018b-fc5e-d330-a9bb-ffded9a60000</guid></item><item><title>以色列与哈马斯的战争已经蔓延到纽约的烹饪界</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-23/ty-article/.premium/the-israel-hamas-war-has-spilled-into-n-y-c-s-cuisine-scene/0000018b-fc6c-d330-a9bb-fffeb1540000</link><description>纽约市的以色列餐馆正面临抵制、反以色列涂鸦和在线分享“犹太复国主义餐馆”地点的呼声。以色列餐馆老板声称他们没有被吓倒</description><pubDate>Thu, 23 Nov 2023 16:30:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-23/ty-article/.premium/the-israel-hamas-war-has-spilled-into-n-y-c-s-cuisine-scene/0000018b-fc6c-d330-a9bb-fffeb1540000</guid></item><item><title>对于埃及来说，其在以色列与哈马斯谈判中的作用事关国家安全</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-23/ty-article/.premium/for-egypt-its-role-in-israel-hamas-negotiations-is-a-matter-of-national-security/0000018b-fc26-d783-a3df-fc3e312e0000</link><description>埃及担心，临时停火后加沙地带南部战火重燃，将导致加沙人大规模移民埃及。除了外交努力外，埃及军队正在加强边境，以防止这种情况发生</description><pubDate>Thu, 23 Nov 2023 16:18:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-23/ty-article/.premium/for-egypt-its-role-in-israel-hamas-negotiations-is-a-matter-of-national-security/0000018b-fc26-d783-a3df-fc3e312e0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列逮捕加沙Al-Shifa主任：“监督医院被用作哈马斯总部”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-23/ty-article/.premium/israel-arrests-director-of-gazas-al-shifa-oversaw-hospitals-use-as-hamas-hq/0000018b-fccf-d4d0-addf-ffff02850000</link><description>据以色列军方称，哈马斯利用医院的许多资源来运营其在大楼下建造的隧道系统。以色列国防军国际发言人表示，以色列带他只是为了“问几个问题”</description><pubDate>Thu, 23 Nov 2023 16:11:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-23/ty-article/.premium/israel-arrests-director-of-gazas-al-shifa-oversaw-hospitals-use-as-hamas-hq/0000018b-fccf-d4d0-addf-ffff02850000</guid></item><item><title>以色列发言人猛烈抨击天空新闻主持人询问以色列是否“不那么重视巴勒斯坦人的生命”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-23/ty-article/no-equivalence-between-israeli-hostages-and-palestinian-prisoners-says-govt-spokesperson/0000018b-fc9b-d8d0-a58f-ffdb88fe0000</link><description>天空新闻主持人指责以色列没有像以色列人那样重视巴勒斯坦人的生命，因为交换比例为 3:1。政府发言人艾隆·利维（Eylon Levy）：“这是一项令人震惊的指控，如果我们可以为每一名人质释放一名囚犯，我们显然会这么做”</description><pubDate>Thu, 23 Nov 2023 16:07:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-23/ty-article/no-equivalence-between-israeli-hostages-and-palestinian-prisoners-says-govt-spokesperson/0000018b-fc9b-d8d0-a58f-ffdb88fe0000</guid></item></channel></rss>